==English==
===Pronunciation===
*{{audio|en-us-inspect.ogg|Audio (US)}}

===Etymology===
Latin '''[[inspicere]]''' (participial stem ''inspect-),'' literally "look into": [[in]] “in” + [[specere]] “look at.”

===Verb===
'''inspect'''
#to [[examine]] [[critically]] or [[carefully]]; especially, to search out [[problems]] or determine [[condition]]; to [[scrutinize]]
#:'''''Inspect''' the system for leaks.''
#to view and examine [[officially]]
#:''He '''inspected''' the troops and their barracks.''

